ysically connected to the network infrastructure via wires  VMI offers two separate wireless networks   VMI Guest  and  VMI Sentinel  VMI Guest is open to public and visitors to VMI  VMI Sentinel is limited to VMI faculty  staff and cadets  You must have valid VMI logon credentials to connect to VMI Sentinel  Please refer to Connecting to Wireless for instructions on connecting to either of the available VMI wireless networks  Please contact the Help Desk at 7643 with questions regarding the wireless network  Wireless Connecting to Wireless Who has access  Wireless Security VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 